# DATABASE ARCHITECTURE

---

# 1. categories TABLE

Main vehicle types.

Example:

* Bike
* Car
* Bus

## Fields

```plaintext
id
name
slug
icon
status
created_at
updated_at
```

---

# 2. subcategories TABLE

Vehicle brands.

Example:

Bike → Hero

Bike → Honda

Car → Hyundai

## Fields

```plaintext
id
category_id
name
slug
logo
status
created_at
updated_at
```

---

# 3. vehicles TABLE

Main vehicle data.

## Fields

```plaintext
id
category_id
subcategory_id
title
slug
price
discount_price
manufacturer_year
fuel_type
km_driven
thumbnail
description
featured
status
created_at
updated_at
```

---

# 4. vehicle_gallery TABLE

Multiple images + videos.

## Fields

```plaintext
id
vehicle_id
file
type
sort_order
created_at
updated_at
```

type:

```plaintext
image
video
```

---

# 5. enquiries TABLE

WhatsApp enquiry records.

## Fields

```plaintext
id
vehicle_id
name
city
phone
message
created_at
```

---

# 6. settings TABLE

Website settings.

## Fields

```plaintext
id
site_name
logo
whatsapp_number
facebook
instagram
youtube
email
address
```

